## Database Schema

### Tables

#### pre_production
Manages pre-production phase with 12 status checkpoints:
- Couple Name, Client Email, Event Type, Event Date
- Referral Program, Advance/Retainer, Welcome Call, Team Booking
- Story Designing Call, Heartfelt Email, Terms Confirmation, Invoicing
- JD Sending, Music Choice, Invitation Video, WhatsApp Group

#### on_production
Tracks on-production day activities:
- Couple Name, Event Date, Phone Number
- Client Review, Payment Received, BTS Shoot
- Hospitality Gesture, Story Sheet Reference, Team Checklist
- Team Members, Team Feedback

#### post_production
Manages post-production deliverables (18 trackable items):
- Data Copy, Best Couple Edits, Raw Images
- Save the Date, Invite, Countdown
- Celebrity AI Reel, Teaser, Film, Reel, Full Length
- Image Selection, Poster, Album Selection, Photobook
- Digital Portfolio, Payment Recovery

#### checklists
Role-based responsibility tracking:
- Equipment Status, Traditional Videographer/Photographer
- Candid Photographer, Cinematographer, Drone Shooter
- Pre-Wedding Shoot, Team Assignment, Status Management

---

## Module Overview

### 1. Dashboard
- **KPI Cards:** Total records by module
- **Status Alerts:** Pending tasks, overdue items, upcoming events
- **Summary Tables:** Recent records and overdue post-production tasks
- **Quick Statistics:** At-a-glance project status

### 2. Pre-Production Module (`/pre-production`)
- List all pre-production records with search
- Add new client intake records
- Edit existing records
- View detailed status with progress bar
- Delete records
- Completion tracking (0-100%)

### 3. On-Production Module (`/on-production`)
- Team coordination dashboard
- Real-time event day status tracking
- Payment status indicators
- Team member assignment
- Feedback management

### 4. Post-Production Module (`/post-production`)
- 18-point deliverable checklist
- Deadline tracking with overdue alerts
- Delivery status progression
- Completion percentage tracking
- Project closure documentation

### 5. Checklist Module (`/checklist`)
- Equipment readiness tracking
- Role-based responsibility assignment
- Team member coordination
- Detailed role notes
- Status management (Pending/In-Progress/Completed)

---

## API Endpoints

### Dashboard
- `GET /dashboard/` - View dashboard

### Pre-Production
- `GET /pre-production/` - List records
- `GET /pre-production/add` - Add form
- `POST /pre-production/add` - Create record
- `GET /pre-production/{id}` - View record
- `GET /pre-production/{id}/edit` - Edit form
- `POST /pre-production/{id}/edit` - Update record
- `POST /pre-production/{id}/delete` - Delete record

### On-Production
- `GET /on-production/` - List records
- `GET /on-production/add` - Add form
- `POST /on-production/add` - Create record
- `GET /on-production/{id}` - View record
- `GET /on-production/{id}/edit` - Edit form
- `POST /on-production/{id}/edit` - Update record
- `POST /on-production/{id}/delete` - Delete record

### Post-Production
- `GET /post-production/` - List records
- `GET /post-production/add` - Add form
- `POST /post-production/add` - Create record
- `GET /post-production/{id}` - View record
- `GET /post-production/{id}/edit` - Edit form
- `POST /post-production/{id}/edit` - Update record
- `POST /post-production/{id}/delete` - Delete record

### Checklist
- `GET /checklist/` - List checklists
- `GET /checklist/add` - Add form
- `POST /checklist/add` - Create checklist
- `GET /checklist/{id}` - View checklist
- `GET /checklist/{id}/edit` - Edit form
- `POST /checklist/{id}/edit` - Update checklist
- `POST /checklist/{id}/delete` - Delete checklist

