## Configuration

Edit `app/config.py` to customize:

```python
# Database
SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URL = "mssql+pyodbc://..."

# App Settings
APP_TITLE = "ProductionFlow CRM"
DEBUG = True
RELOAD = True

# Upload Settings
MAX_FILE_SIZE = 10 * 1024 * 1024
ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS = {"pdf", "doc", "docx", "jpg", "jpeg", "png"}

# Session
SESSION_TIMEOUT = 3600
```

